T1  - Human Resource Planning: Proposal for a New Journal
AU  - Walker, James W.
Y1  - 1972/06/01
PY  - 1972
DA  - 1972/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amj.1972.17400503
DO  - 10.5465/amj.1972.17400503
